{"id":79,"date":"2025-02-13T15:27:24","date_gmt":"2025-02-13T18:27:24","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thebootstrapthemes.com\/previews\/fitness-pro\/?page_id=2"},"modified":"2026-03-13T14:38:40","modified_gmt":"2026-03-13T17:38:40","slug":"home","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/sefaa.dgac.gob.cl\/","title":{"rendered":"Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-stretch is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\">\n<p><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Te damos la bienvenida<\/strong><\/h1>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Somos la <strong>Secci\u00f3n de Estudios de Fen\u00f3menos A\u00e9reos An\u00f3malos <\/strong>(SEFAA, antiguamente \u00abCEFAA\u00bb), un organismo dependiente de la Direcci\u00f3n General de Aeron\u00e1utica Civil (DGAC) de Chile.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nos dedicamos a investigar los <strong>fen\u00f3menos a\u00e9reos an\u00f3malos o no identificados<\/strong> que puedan presentarse en el espacio a\u00e9reo chileno.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nuestra misi\u00f3n es clara: <strong>apoyar la seguridad de las operaciones a\u00e9reas de nuestro pa\u00eds<\/strong>, mediante el estudio detallado de cada reporte recibido. Cada avistamiento, ya sea de un piloto, un tripulante de cabina o un ciudadano, tiene un valor fundamental para ayudar a garantizar la seguridad en nuestro cielo.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tu experiencia es importante para nosotros<\/strong>. Si has sido testigo de alg\u00fan fen\u00f3meno a\u00e9reo que te pareci\u00f3 inusual, te invitamos a <strong>compartir tu reporte<\/strong>. Estar\u00e1s contribuyendo directamente a un an\u00e1lisis serio y profesional.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:50%\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-video\"><video height=\"1080\" style=\"aspect-ratio: 1920 \/ 1080;\" width=\"1920\" controls muted poster=\"https:\/\/sefaa.dgac.gob.cl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/SEFAA-video-cover.png\" src=\"https:\/\/sefaa.dgac.gob.cl\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/02\/SEFAA-1.mp4\"><\/video><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Te damos la bienvenida Somos la Secci\u00f3n de Estudios de Fen\u00f3menos A\u00e9reos An\u00f3malos (SEFAA, antiguamente&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":27,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-79","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sefaa.dgac.gob.cl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/79","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sefaa.dgac.gob.cl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sefaa.dgac.gob.cl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sefaa.dgac.gob.cl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/27"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sefaa.dgac.gob.cl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=79"}],"version-history":[{"count":63,"href":"https:\/\/sefaa.dgac.gob.cl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/79\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3555,"href":"https:\/\/sefaa.dgac.gob.cl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/79\/revisions\/3555"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/sefaa.dgac.gob.cl\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=79"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}